- A13 CELL + PLACED ( 30 150 ) N ;
- A14 CELL + PLACED ( 70 150 ) N ;
- A15 CELL + PLACED ( 110 150 ) N ;
- A16 CELL + PLACED ( 150 150 ) N ;
- B1 CELL + PLACED ( 290 30 ) N ;
