- B9 CELL + PLACED ( 290 110 ) N ;
- B10 CELL + PLACED ( 330 110 ) N ;
- B11 CELL + PLACED ( 370 110 ) N ;
- B12 CELL + PLACED ( 410 110 ) N ;
- B13 CELL + PLACED ( 290 150 ) N ;
- B14 CELL + PLACED ( 330 150 ) N ;
- B15 CELL + PLACED ( 370 150 ) N ;
- B16 CELL + PLACED ( 410 150 ) N ;
END COMPONENTS

PINS 4 ;
- inA + NET inA + DIRECTION INPUT + USE SIGNAL + PLACED ( 0 250 ) N ;
- inB + NET inB + DIRECTION INPUT + USE SIGNAL + PLACED ( 500 250 ) N ;
- outA + NET outA + DIRECTION OUTPUT + USE SIGNAL + PLACED ( 0 100 ) N ;
- outB + NET outB + DIRECTION OUTPUT + USE SIGNAL + PLACED ( 500 100 ) N ;
END PINS

NETS 34 ;
- inA ( PIN inA ) ( A1 A ) ;
- hubA_fan ( A1 Y ) ( A2 B ) ( A3 B ) ( A4 B ) ( A5 B ) ( A6 B ) ( A7 B ) ( A8 B ) ( A9 B ) ( A10 B ) ( A11 B ) ( A12 B ) ( A13 B ) ( A14 B ) ( A15 B ) ( A16 B ) ;
- ringA0 ( A2 Y ) ( A3 A ) ;
- ringA1 ( A3 Y ) ( A4 A ) ;
- ringA2 ( A4 Y ) ( A5 A ) ;
- ringA3 ( A5 Y ) ( A6 A ) ;
- ringA4 ( A6 Y ) ( A7 A ) ;
- ringA5 ( A7 Y ) ( A8 A ) ;
- ringA6 ( A8 Y ) ( A9 A ) ;
- ringA7 ( A9 Y ) ( A10 A ) ;
- ringA8 ( A10 Y ) ( A11 A ) ;
- ringA9 ( A11 Y ) ( A12 A ) ;
- ringA10 ( A12 Y ) ( A13 A ) ;
- ringA11 ( A13 Y ) ( A14 A ) ;
- ringA12 ( A14 Y ) ( A15 A ) ;
- ringA13 ( A15 Y ) ( A16 A ) ;
- inB ( PIN inB ) ( B1 A ) ;
- hubB_fan ( B1 Y ) ( B2 B ) ( B3 B ) ( B4 B ) ( B5 B ) ( B6 B ) ( B7 B ) ( B8 B ) ( B9 B ) ( B10 B ) ( B11 B ) ( B12 B ) ( B13 B ) ( B14 B ) ( B15 B ) ( B16 B ) ;
- ringB0 ( B2 Y ) ( B3 A ) ;
- ringB1 ( B3 Y ) ( B4 A ) ;
- ringB2 ( B4 Y ) ( B5 A ) ;
- ringB3 ( B5 Y ) ( B6 A ) ;
- ringB4 ( B6 Y ) ( B7 A ) ;
