- ringB10 ( B12 Y ) ( B13 A ) ;
- ringB11 ( B13 Y ) ( B14 A ) ;
- ringB12 ( B14 Y ) ( B15 A ) ;
- ringB13 ( B15 Y ) ( B16 A ) ;
- outB ( B16 Y ) ( PIN outB ) ;
- outA ( A16 Y ) ( PIN outA ) ( B1 B ) ;
END NETS

END DESIGN
